# Flutter Standards

- Use `final` and `const` where possible
- Trailing commas on multi-line calls
- Resolve dependencies via `getIt<T>()`
- Register in appropriate DI module (network, repository, domain, presentation)
- Handle errors with typed `ApiException`
- Import order: dart, flutter, packages, project
